>> The metric to evaluate a bounding box is called ________ and it is the ratio of ________ over ________. <<

( ) Structured output, area of overlap, area of union  {{ The metric is called intersection over union }}
( ) Union over intersection, area of overlap, area of union  {{ The metric is called intersection over union, not union over intersection }}
(x) Intersection over union, area of overlap, area of union 
( ) Intersection over union, area of union, area of overlap  {{ The ratio is the area of overlap over area of union }}

